{{> header}}

<h2>Order Receipt</h2>
<p>Dear {{orderDetails.orderDetails.payer.name.given_name}},</p> <!-- Using given_name from PayPal details -->

<p>Thank you for your purchase. Here's a summary of your order:</p>

<h3>Order Details:</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Order ID:</strong> {{orderDetails.orderDetails.id}}</li>
    <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{dateFormat orderDetails.orderDetails.create_time "MMMM D, YYYY, h:mm A"}}</li>
    <li><strong>Total Amount:</strong> ${{orderDetails.orderDetails.purchase_units.[0].amount.value}}</li>
</ul>

<h3>Items Purchased:</h3>
<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
    <tr>
        <th style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">Item</th>
        <th style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">Quantity</th>
        <th style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px; text-align: left;">Price</th>
    </tr>
    {{#each orderDetails.cartContents}}
    <tr>
        <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;">{{this.event.name}} on {{dateFormat this.event.date "MMMM D, YYYY"}} at {{formatDateWithTimeZone this.event.date "h:mm A z" "America/New_York"}}</td>
        <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;">{{this.enrollees.length}}</td>
        <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;">${{this.event.price}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/each}}
</table>

<p>If you have any questions about your order, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>

<p>Thank you for your business!</p>

{{> footer}}